"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-09-07-Olympic-commemorative-sculpture-donated-by-CMG-inaugurated-in-France-1wHGJsEDF2o-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Sports Scene  Copied  People in attendance for the Olympic sculpture's launching ceremony in Noisy-le-Grand, France. /CMG  China Media Group (CMG) has donated a commemorative sculpture named \\\"Rowing in the Same Boat\\\" to the French National Olympic and Sports Committee.  The sculpture was inaugurated on Friday along with a ceremony of the \\\"Olympic Peace Park\\\" in the French city of Noisy-le-Grand.  China's ambassador to France, the Chief Cultural Officer of the French National Olympic Committee and the Mayor of Noisy-le-Grand attended the event and delivered speeches. The sculpture integrates cultural symbols of both China and France, symbolizing the friendship between the two sides.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"